Simply don't run any async code on GeneratorExit.
Used async functions should also be careful about it.

```python
async def gen():
    try:
        for i in range(10):
            yield (await some_async_func())
    except GeneratorExit:
        print('Generator Exited')
        raise
    except:
        await sleep(10)
```

